	   <tr><td colspan=2>FD with skill or spell always has a chance of failure even if you are out of melee although the chance of the mob seeing through the spell does seem to go down with range. If one MOB sees through the others soon will. Also if any caster has started a spell and you feign before the spell hits you it will automatically see through the FD. If you start to FD and see a caster MOB start a spell towards you you might as well move and interupt your spell and retry. Hope that is helpful.<br><br>Malegrim Troll SK<br>Sithkar Iskar monk<br>Shadowmane Human necro<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
